<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	{{> html-head title="Product Card" }}
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container text-center my-5 customer-reviews">

		<h2 class="h1 mb-4">What customers say about our Pink Clay Mask.</h2>

        <div id="carouselLoop" class="carousel slide carousel--loop row mb-3" data-slide-number="3">
			<div class="carousel--centered">
				<div class="carousel-inner d-flex flex-nowrap" role="listbox">
                    {{#times 6}}
                    <figure class="carousel-item review-card col-9 col-lg-4 {{#if @first}}active{{/if}}">
                        <picture class="d-block">
                            <source srcset="https://via.placeholder.com/370x370?text={{@index}}" media="(min-width: 992px)">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/280x280?text={{@index}}" alt="Placeholder" class="d-block w-100">
                        </picture>
                        <figcaption class="mt-n2 mx-g p-g p-lg-3 text-center position-relative font-size-sm">
                            <p>To all the ladies out there who are just having a bad skin day like me today, I wouldnâ€™t look any further than this wonderful tub of magic by @sandandskyaus I absolutely adore this magic potion pink clay mask and just to let you know this is my second tub<br>-<br>@nichole.47</p>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    {{/times}}

				</div>
			</div>
			<a class="carousel-control carousel-control-prev carousel-control--background carousel-control--loop" href="#carouselLoop" role="button" data-slide="prev">
				<span class="carousel-control-prev-icon sni sni__chevron-prev justify-content-center align-items-center" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
			</a>
			<a class="carousel-control carousel-control-next carousel-control--background carousel-control--loop" href="#carouselLoop" role="button" data-slide="next">
				<span class="carousel-control-next-icon sni sni__chevron-next justify-content-center align-items-center" aria-hidden="true"></span>
				<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	{{> js jquery=true bootstrap=true main=true }}
</body>

</html>
